elements.name: Como usuario verifico que el post esté creado sin tags, y despues aparezca el tag

steps.name: I wait for a signal containing "logged" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "creating tag" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "tag created" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "creating" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "posting" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "post created" for 30 seconds
I navigate to page "<HOST>"
I select the post with title "$$name_2"
I check the post name "$$name_2"
I send a signal to user 1 containing "checking"
I wait for 2 seconds
I check the post content "$$string_1"
I check the tag "$$name_1" does not exist
I send a signal to user 1 containing "checked notag"
I wait for 2 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "editing" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "tagging" for 30 seconds
I wait for a signal containing "post tagged" for 30 seconds
I refresh the site
I check the tag "$$name_1" exists
